FogBugz
========

Install Notes
-------------

Be sure to set up your FogBugz installation to handle multiple 
repositories/multiple source control systems as described in
http://www.fogcreek.com/FogBugz/KB/howto/MultipleRepositories-Mult.html

  1. cvssubmit_url is the url to the cvsSubmit.[php|asp] file on your FogBugz server.
     Example: https://server.com/fogbugz/cvsSubmit.php
  2. The "sRepo" field will be set to the name of the github repo.


Developer Notes
---------------

data
  - cvssubmit_url
  
payload
  - refer to docs/github_payload
